    public abstract class AbstractBase40<E extends AbstractBase40<E>>
extends AbstractLightweightBase40<E>
implements CharSequence
    AbstractBase40 represents an abstract base class for 64bit non-negative base-40 values. For a description of the base-40 encoding, see Base40.
